content: Single Frame - Installation Manual Physical Planning, GC28-7040-00, https://www-40.ibm.com/servers/resourcelink/lib03010.nsf/pagesByDocid/872B572FB04B48 6A852588E700492CAB?OpenDocument The power estimation tool for the z16 A02 allows you to enter your precise and detailed configuration to obtain an estimate of power consumption. Log in to the Resource link with your user ID. Click Planning → Tools → Power and weight estimation. Specify the quantity for the features that are installed in your system. This tool estimates the power consumption for the specified configuration. The tool does not verify that the specified configuration can be physically built.
